  <!-- Síntesis de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Display samples of student work for each problem next to each other, including a sample of a drawing of equal groups and a sample of a tape diagram.</li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Dónde encontramos las partes del problema en el dibujo y en el diagrama?</q>  (The number of objects in each group are the dots in the drawing, but the number is written in each part of the diagram.)
      </li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Cómo usaron los factores de cada ecuación para encontrar el producto?</q>  (The factors told me how many groups there were and how many were in each group.)
      </li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Cómo les ayudan los dibujos y los diagramas a encontrar la solución del problema?</q>  (You can count the dots in the drawing. The diagram can be used to count by 10.)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


